            "sidebar_type": "related_creatures",
            "sidebar_heading": "Related Creatures",
            "image": {
                "type": "image",
                "name": "Related Creatures",
                "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
            },
            "html": "The elasmosaurus is but one of many types of aquatic reptiles found in primeval oceans or lost worlds. Some, like the ichthyosaurus, are almost fishlike in appearance. Others, such as the mosasaurus, are truly massive beasts capable of killing and eating whales."
        }
